1. *Trenutka* se okrenula i nestala u mnoštvu ljudi. (In a moment she turned and disappeared in the crowd.) 
2. Svi smo čekali *trenutak* kada će se nešto desiti. (We all waited for the moment when something would happen.) 
3. U tom *trenutku* je shvatila da je pogrešila. (At that moment she realised that she had made a mistake.) 
4. *Trenutke* kada se sve zaustavi i nema nikakvog zvuka. (The moments when everything stops and there is no sound.) 
5. Ona je uživala u *trenutku* u tišini. (She enjoyed the moment of silence.) 
6. Oni su se suočili sa *trenutkom* istine. (They faced the moment of truth.)